{"id":8,"date":"2025-05-02T18:38:34","date_gmt":"2025-05-02T18:38:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jbx.ail.mybluehost.me\/website_02d9b540\/?page_id=8"},"modified":"2026-03-10T23:31:40","modified_gmt":"2026-03-10T17:31:40","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.6&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; background_image=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Untitled-design-6.png&#8221; min_height_tablet=&#8221;&#8221; min_height_phone=&#8221;&#8221; min_height_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;50px||||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;||54px|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; positioning=&#8221;none&#8221; position_origin_a=&#8221;center_center&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;32vh|auto||auto|false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.6&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_text_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; text_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; header_font=&#8221;Montserrat Alternates||||||||&#8221; header_text_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;49px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{%22gcid-64840f85-baf8-4549-a37c-c6c9c34ff86f%22:%91%22text_text_shadow_color%22%93}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h1 class=\"preFade fadeIn\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_587\">ABA Therapy and Autism Diagnosis in Bountiful &amp; Draper, Utah<\/h1>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.6&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_text_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; text_font_size=&#8221;21px&#8221; text_line_height=&#8221;1.8em&#8221; header_text_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{%22gcid-64840f85-baf8-4549-a37c-c6c9c34ff86f%22:%91%22text_text_shadow_color%22%93}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Locally owned provider with no waitlist for autism evaluations \u2013 accepting new ABA therapy clients for morning and daytime hours.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_2_text_align=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"preFade fadeIn\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_603\"><a href=\"#yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_603\">Our Program<\/a><\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_font_size=&#8221;23px&#8221; text_line_height=&#8221;1.8em&#8221; text_orientation=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-01aca4c3815196ff78a8\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_597\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-01aca4c3815196ff78a8\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_605\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_604\">\n<p class=\"sqsrte-large preFade fadeIn\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746211386294_610\">Kuska Autism Services offers a blend of direct ABA therapy, cooperative efforts with parents, evaluations, and assistance within the community. Our skilled professionals design tailored treatment strategies focusing on developing communication, social skills, and independence, utilizing proven methodologies. We are committed to ongoing support for our community.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Add-a-heading-18.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Add a heading (18)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||0px||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_3_text_align=&#8221;center&#8221; header_3_font_size=&#8221;26px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>Social Skills<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Add-a-heading-17.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Add a heading (17)&#8221; _builder_version=&#82